</div> </section> <section class="lead-capture" id="momentum-score"> <div class="container"> <h2>Take the 3-Minute <span>Architecture Score</span></h2> <p>Get a fast read on where your positioning, offer, and demand system are leaking value right now.</p> <a href="#" class="btn btn-gold"> <i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i> Apply for Private Advisory </a> <span class="micro-assurance">Fast diagnostic. Clear next steps. No generic playbook.</span> </div> </section> <section class="lead-capture" style="background: var(--cream);"> <div class="container"> <h2>Investment</h2> <p class="section-sub" style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 20px;">REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> is priced for transformation, not hourly advice. Every engagement starts with fit, then moves into architecture.</p> <a href="#momentum-score" class="btn btn-gold"> <i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i> Apply for Private Advisory </a> <span class="micro-assurance">Limited private slots each month. Qualified applicants only.</span> </div> </section> <section class="faq"> <div class="container"> <h2>Frequently <span>Asked</span></h2> <p class="section-sub">Common questions about working with REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> Advisors.</p> <div class="faq-list"> <div class="faq-item"> <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"> <h4>Who is REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> for?</h4> <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i> </div> <div class="faq-answer"> <p>REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> is for experienced professionals with 10+ years of expertise who are ready to monetize their knowledge. You should have deep experience in your field and be willing to package it into a structured offer. This is not for those looking for quick fixes — it's for professionals ready to build a real, scalable asset.</p> </div> </div> <div class="faq-item"> <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"> <h4>Do I need a business idea already?</h4> <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i> </div> <div class="faq-answer"> <p>No. You bring the experience — we bring the structure. Many of our clients have expertise but no clear business idea. We help you identify what you've actually built and how to package it. You don't need a plan; you need experience and willingness to do the work.</p> </div> </div> <div class="faq-item"> <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"> <h4>Is this a course or consulting retainer?</h4> <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i> </div> <div class="faq-answer"> <p>No. REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> is private Intellectual Asset Architecture. It is not a course, not a cohort, and not an open-ended consulting retainer. The work is structured, category-first, and outcome-defined.</p> </div> </div> <div class="faq-item"> <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"> <h4>How long is the engagement?</h4> <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i> </div> <div class="faq-answer"> <p>The core engagement is designed to deliver clarity within 30 days and a market-ready offer within 90 days. However, the exact timeline depends on your starting position and the complexity of your expertise. Strategic advisory continues throughout to ensure your asset evolves with market opportunities.</p> </div> </div> <div class="faq-item"> <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"> <h4>What do I leave with?</h4> <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i> </div> <div class="faq-answer"> <p>You leave with a clearly defined strategic advisory asset, a precise audience willing to pay, a structured sellable offer, and premium-aligned positioning. You'll have a repeatable system that converts expertise into revenue and scales beyond your time.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class="final-cta"> <div class="container"> <h2>Ready to Turn Experience Into a Premium Offer?</h2> <p>Apply for a private advisory fit check and map the next 90 days around a structured offer and stronger demand.</p> <a href="#momentum-score" class="btn btn-gold"> <i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i> Apply for Private Advisory </a> <span class="micro-assurance">Limited private slots each month. Qualified applicants only.</span> </div> </section> <footer> <div class="container"> <div class="logo-group"> <div class="logo-mark"> <span class="logo">REIGNITE</span><span class="logo-dot">.</span> </div> <span class="logo-sub">Advisors</span> </div> <p class="tagline">Transform expertise into impact.</p> <p class="copyright">&copy; 2025 Reignite Advisors. All rights reserved.</p> </div> </footer> <script> function scrollCarousel(direction) { const track = document.getElementById('resultsCarousel'); const card = track.querySelector('.carousel-card'); const cardWidth = card.offsetWidth + 20; track.scrollBy({ left: direction * cardWidth, behavior: 'smooth' }); } function toggleFaq(element) { const faqItem = element.parentElement; faqItem.classList.toggle('active'); } </script> </body>
